val factsDS = spark.table("traffic.facts").select("local_authority_ons_code", "date_id", "hour", "count")
val authoritiesDS = spark.table("traffic.authorities").select("local_authority_ons_code", "region_name")

    join(datesDS, factsDS("date_id") === datesDS("id")).
    groupBy((floor(datesDS("year")/10) * 10).as("decades"), factsDS("hour")).
    agg(sum("count").as("sumOfAll"))

Analiza 2

Porównanie wartości procentowej ilosci przejazdow w poszczegolnychr regionach przy poszczegolnej pogodzie dla wybranych kategorii pojazdow

paragraphs.text:
val factsDS = spark.table("traffic.facts").select("local_authority_ons_code", "weather_id", "vehicle_type_id", "count")
val authoritiesDS = spark.table("traffic.authorities").select("local_authority_ons_code", "region_name")
val weathersDS = spark.table("traffic.weathers").select("id", "weather")
val vehicle_typesDS = spark.table("traffic.vehicle_types").select("type_id", "type_name")

msg.data:
factsDS: org.apache.spark.sql.DataFrame = [local_authority_ons_code: string, weather_id: int ... 2 more fields]
authoritiesDS: org.apache.spark.sql.DataFrame = [local_authority_ons_code: string, region_name: string]
weathersDS: org.apache.spark.sql.DataFrame = [id: int, weather: string]
vehicle_typesDS: org.apache.spark.sql.DataFrame = [type_id: int, type_name: string]

paragraphs.text:
val sumaPrzejazdowDlaPoszczegolnychTypowPojazdow = factsDS.
    join(authoritiesDS, factsDS("local_authority_ons_code") === authoritiesDS("local_authority_ons_code")).
    join(vehicle_typesDS, factsDS("vehicle_type_id") === vehicle_typesDS("type_id")).
    groupBy(vehicle_typesDS("type_name")).
    agg(sum("count").as("totalDlaPojazdu"))

val analiza2_DS = factsDS.
    join(authoritiesDS, factsDS("local_authority_ons_code") === authoritiesDS("local_authority_ons_code")).
    join(weathersDS, factsDS("weather_id") === weathersDS("id")).
    join(vehicle_typesDS, factsDS("vehicle_type_id") === vehicle_typesDS("type_id")).
    join(sumaPrzejazdowDlaPoszczegolnychTypowPojazdow, vehicle_typesDS("type_name") === sumaPrzejazdowDlaPoszczegolnychTypowPojazdow("type_name")).
    groupBy(weathersDS("weather"), vehicle_typesDS("type_name")).
    agg((sum("count")/(avg("totalDlaPojazdu"))).as("procentPrzejazdowDanegoTypuWDanaPogode"))
